#Search Results

In sitefinity search results can not be modified through the widget editor. Below is a generic styling of the search results page

##Example CSS
```SCSS

.sfsearchResultTitle{
	display:block;
	margin-top:15px; //Give some space from the result above
	padding-top:10px; 
	font-size:1.3em;
	border-top:1px solid #cccccc;
	font-weight:bold;
}
.sfsearchResultHighLighter{
	margin-left:0px;
	background:lighten($color-primary, 28%);
	padding:10px;
}
.sfsearchResultUrl {
	margin-left: 0px;
	padding: 5px 0;
	position:relative;
	&:before{
		content:'URL: ';
		padding-right:10px;
	}
}

```
